&lt;li&gt;Improve test coverage of existing codebases as well as engage in test-driven development practices with the team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in architecting new cryptocurrency and wallet infrastructure relying on modern standards and practices.&lt;/li&gt;
